          <div class="strategy-tip">
            <strong>Exam strategy:</strong> The Agile Manifesto has four value pairs — the left side is valued <em>more</em>, the right side is <em>not rejected</em>. Many MCQs will flip the sides to trick you. Memorize all four left-over-right pairs.
