              <li><strong>&cross; Following a plan <em>over</em> Responding to change</strong> &mdash; Reversed. The manifesto values "Responding to change over Following a plan."</li>
              <li><strong>&cross; Contract negotiation <em>over</em> Customer collaboration</strong> &mdash; Reversed. The manifesto values "Customer collaboration over Contract negotiation."</li>
              <li><strong>&cross; Comprehensive documentation <em>over</em> Working software</strong> &mdash; Reversed. The manifesto values "Working software over Comprehensive documentation."</li>
